<div class="row u-mb-5">
   <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h2>Building Forms</h2>
    <p>Often you'll want to combine these components to create larger forms.</p>
    <p>For this we have the <code>fieldset</code> and <code>legend</code> tags. Fieldset defines a set of components that are in a certain group. Legend is the label for that group. Following is an example of creating a form using these fields.</p>

    <h3>Form Validation</h3>
    <p>We take advantage of a forms <code>required</code> attribute which will check for a <code>pattern</code> attribute and base validation of the pattern's regex rules. If no pattern is found, it assumes that the field cannot be left blank.</p>
    <p>Select boxes are validated by wraping the select in <code>.is-requiredSelect</code>. There must be a blank option and a <code>data-placeholder="Choose an Option"</code> on the select element.</p>
   </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <div class="example">
      <form data-validate="true">
        <fieldset>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="small-6 columns">
              <input type="text" placeholder="First name" title="must be 5 or more characters" pattern=".{4,}" required>
            </div>
            <div class="small-6 columns">
              <input type="text" placeholder="Last name" required>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row u-mb-2">
            <div class="small-12 columns">
              <textarea type="textarea" placeholder="Notes" required></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row u-mb-4">
            <div class="small-6 columns">
              <div class="formGroup required">
                <div class="checkbox">
                  <input type='checkbox' name='chackbox' value='' id="checkboxy"/>
                  <span></span>
                  <label for="checkboxy">Option A</label>
                </div>
                <div class="checkbox">
                  <input type='checkbox' name='chackbox' value='' id="checkboxyB"/>
                  <span></span>
                  <label for="checkboxyB">Option B</label>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="small-6 columns">
              <div class="is-requiredSelect">
                <select data-placeholder="Choose a fruit" class="select chosen">
                  <option class="placeholder" value=""></option>
                  <option value="Apples">Apples</option>
                  <option value="Mangos">Mangos</option>
                  <option value="Pears">Pears</option>
                  <option value="Plums">Plums</option>
                  <option value="Nectarine">Nectarine</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>
        <input type="submit" value="Submit Verification Request" class="Button Button--blue Button--fullWidth" disabled>
      </form>
    </div>
